# Write a band name generator program so it asks you for a city that you grew up in and the name of your pet and then it combines those together and gives you the name of your band.

#1. Create a greeting for your program.
print("Welcome to the Band generator!")
#2. Ask the user for the city that they grew up in.
city = input("Which city do yo grew up in?\n")
#3. Ask the user for the name of a pet.
pet = input("What is the name of your pet?\n")
#4. Combine the name of their city and pet and show them their band name.
print("Your brand's name could be: " + city + " " + pet)

